                    ],
                    Texts: [
                        {
                            Text: "Hold at the fence, resident. Frostfallow is a managed agricultural asset. Foot traffic through the frozen rows is unlicensed commerce, and unlicensed commerce is a conversation with me."
                        },
                        {
                            Text: "The family that used to work this pass has been transitioned. The crop belongs to the Company now, and the Company does not do trespass. It does engagements. Would you like one in the snow?"
                        }
                    ],
                    Name: "Officer - the fence",
                    Label: "fence_hail"
                },
